description: Lists all available signing profiles in your AWS account. Returns only profiles with an ACTIVE status unless the includeCanceled request field is set to true. If additional jobs remain to be listed, AWS Signer returns a nextToken value. Use this value in subsequent calls to ListSigningJobs to fetch the remaining values. You can continue calling ListSigningJobs with your maxResults parameter and with new values that Signer returns in the nextToken parameter until all of your signing jobs have been returned.

parameters.name: statuses
parameters.description: Filters results to return only signing jobs with statuses in the specified list. (string) ---

nested_items.name: profiles
nested_items.description: A list of profiles that are available in the AWS account. This includes profiles with the status of CANCELED if the includeCanceled parameter is set to true.

nested_items.name: profileName
nested_items.description: The name of the signing profile.

nested_items.name: profileVersion
nested_items.description: The version of a signing profile.

nested_items.name: profileVersionArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of a signing profile, including the profile version.

nested_items.name: signingMaterial
nested_items.description: The ACM certificate that is available for use by a signing profile.

nested_items.name: certificateArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the certificates that is used to sign your code.

nested_items.name: signatureValidityPeriod
nested_items.description: The validity period for a signing job created using this signing profile.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The numerical value of the time unit for signature validity.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The time unit for signature validity.

nested_items.name: platformId
nested_items.description: The ID of a platform that is available for use by a signing profile.

nested_items.name: platformDisplayName
nested_items.description: The name of the signing platform.

nested_items.name: signingParameters
nested_items.description: The parameters that are available for use by a Signer user.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of a signing profile.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the signing profile.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: Value for specifying the next set of paginated results to return.
